{"id":7970,"date":"2017-12-18T01:39:55","date_gmt":"2017-12-17T18:39:55","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=7970"},"modified":"2020-02-18T11:27:41","modified_gmt":"2020-02-18T04:27:41","slug":"tu-thiet-ke-logo","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/design\/tu-thiet-ke-logo","title":{"rendered":"T\u1ef1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo cho website trong 5 ph\u00fat"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 <strong>t\u1ef1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo<\/strong> cho website \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ban \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m online mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Logos and branding are so important. In a big part of world, people cannot read French or English, but are great in remembering signs<\/em><\/p><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n tham gia cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i internet business.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i kia, c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng t\u00e1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c logo t\u1eeb d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed h\u1ebft, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ch\u00fang. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 theo t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1eebng lo, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng r\u00e0nh v\u1ec1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt hay thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m theo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Kh\u1edfi t\u1ea1o logo<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o website <a href=\"\/out\/canva\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Canva (opens in a new tab)\">Canva<\/a> \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft, Canva l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf online \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia khuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. Canva d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf banner qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, b\u00eca s\u00e1ch, poster, th\u01b0 m\u1eddi,\u2026 v\u00e0 logo. Sau b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y b\u1ecf th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u Canva v\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 \u00edch cho b\u1ea1n sau n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/1-1024x506.png\"><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/1-1024x506.png\" alt=\"Giao di\u1ec7n Canva\"\/><\/a><figcaption>Giao di\u1ec7n Canva<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ti\u1ebfp theo, b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o m\u1ee5c find template (t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf) v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/4-1024x506.png\"><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/4-1024x506.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0o ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf r\u1ea5t chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p cho b\u1ea1n tha h\u1ed3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn logo n\u00e0o ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u1ede \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn logo NEUE l\u00e0m v\u00ed d\u1ee5 cho b\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/7-1024x506.png\"><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/7-1024x506.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u1ea1i logo<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t logo m\u1eabu \u01b0ng \u00fd. Ti\u1ebfp theo, b\u1ea1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00ean c\u1ee7a logo th\u00e0nh t\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean ph\u00f3ng to logo l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/8-1024x506.png\"><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/8-1024x506.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u00ec t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh. B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y b\u1ea5m n\u00fat download \u1edf b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ph\u00eda tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh. L\u01b0u v\u00e0o m\u00e1y t\u00ednh ngo\u00e0i desktop \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u01b0\u1edbc 3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/9-1024x506.png\"><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/9-1024x506.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: T\u1ea1o n\u1ec1n \u1ea3nh trong su\u1ed1t<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n xu\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1edf \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng PNG (\u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng \u1ea3nh trong su\u1ed1t) nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf n\u1ec1n \u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng trong su\u1ed1t. V\u00ec Canva \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y cho t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. B\u1ea1n bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1ch n\u1ec1n \u1ea3nh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eebng lo, th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi internet lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p thay th\u1ebf. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 <a name=\"http:\/\/www199.lunapic.com\/editor\/\"><\/a><a href=\"http:\/\/www199.lunapic.com\/editor\/\">Lunapic<\/a>. B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y b\u1ea5m v\u00e0o link \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Lunapic.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n v\u00e0o Edit &gt; Transparent background &gt; Choose file<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/10-1024x506.png\"><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/10-1024x506.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn \u1ea3nh m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 l\u01b0u \u1edf b\u01b0\u1edbc 2.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/11-1024x506.png\"><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/11-1024x506.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea5m v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng ra kh\u1ecfi n\u1ec1n \u1ea3nh. \u0110i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh threshold th\u00e0nh 50 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 trong su\u1ed1t cao nh\u1ea5t. Apply threshold.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/12-1024x480.png\"><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/12-1024x480.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n b\u1ea5m save \u0111\u1ec3 l\u01b0u \u1ea3nh l\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 logo \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n r\u1ed3i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/13-1024x480.png\"><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/13-1024x480.png\" alt=\"t\u1ef1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo\"\/><\/a><figcaption>Logo \u0111\u00e3 trong su\u1ed1t<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd khi t\u00e1ch n\u1ec1n:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>N\u1ebfu logo b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u1ec1n \u0111en hay n\u1ec1n m\u00e0u th\u00ec b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y b\u1ecf qua b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y<\/li><li>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1ch n\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m s\u1eeda \u1ea3nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i photoshop, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/li><li>M\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i logo l\u00e0 500x500px<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i&#8230;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1ef1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t logo ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhu c\u1ea7u thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf web c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n. &#8220;Done&#8221; v\u1eabn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 &#8220;Perfect&#8221; \u0111\u00fang kh\u00f4ng n\u00e0o?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u01b0a hi\u1ec3u b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e9.\n<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo cho website \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1e